28323_5885355310176010240_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=66VcW7qyzoIQ7kNvgG_1EEi&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAYcS8uBBfUnziiJyuyw0kSj68hk3C5BIBzIIaYqMN1Vg&oe=66E42BE5"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "12138848_188442018286999_8666111583660802048_n.png", "id": "1815281048689008", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12727931_1815281052022341_2238148303084584960_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Y3Wbt4-pRqgQ7kNvgGjlC5b&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCmPnOzIhx5PWmA6h0DSrdrarWyyycI27nDGPCMdSw8Dw&oe=66E42788"}, "display_name": "SwingStar Demo", "keywords": ["swing", "puzzle", "rope", "swinging", "spiderman"], "long_description": "SwingStar VR allows players to swing around a virtual reality world using a giant sticky hand attached to their head. The game is a third-person swinging physics puzzler that puts players through a wild ride, accelerating the player as they swing. It's wacky and super fun.\n\nA disaster has mutated physics, you must save your home multiverse by ringing all the mysterious bells. A colossus robot stand between you and the final bell.\n\n- Explore all 30 colorful cartoon levels by swinging through enchanted deserts, bright forests, steep canyons, and many more bizarre and beautiful worlds.\n- Epic Boss Battle.\n- Unlock mysterious doors that unlock secret levels\n- Wacky power up items change the gameplay. Turbo Yo-yos swing you around, Air Cannons blast you high in the air, and The Grappling Jelly will suck you to it's gooey surface.\n- Brilliantly dreamy soundtrack.\n- Master each level to receive a perfect 3 Star rank.\n- Get all 84 stars to unlock the mysterious inter-dimensional zone.", "short_description": "SwingStar VR allows players to swing around a virtual reality world using a giant sticky hand attached to their head. The game is a third-person swinging physics puzzler that puts players through a wild ride, accelerating the player as they 